{"tid":2165694,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"請五眼聯盟對所有留任議員施以制裁","createTime":"2020-08-20T03:53:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-20T09:06:36.000Z","uid":217430,"like":23,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"296f9b39227839fcc1d230e76943dfe24376c8ef","tid":2165694,"uid":217430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T03:53:47.000Z","msg":"還有人記得五眼聯盟出過聯合聲明，要求如期進行立法會選舉嗎？<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/news/hong-kong-statement-on-the-erosion-of-rights\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gov.uk%2Fgovernment%2Fnews%2Fhong-kong-statement-on-the-erosion-of-rights&d=MESMej01p5OZpZHaxDRufQ1nSF4GOVyTVdrqrZ1TEh8%3D&h=6b5d4cbe\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.gov.uk/government/news/hong-kong-statement-on-the-erosion-of-rights</a><br />\n<br />\n為什麼五眼這麼緊張？<br />\n<br />\n因為立法會選舉就是一個民意授權，四年舉辦一次就等於民眾的選票只授權代議士四年任期。<br />\n<br />\n任期延長一年，當中並沒有任何民意基礎，只是一個由中共極權政府<span class=\"red\">委任</span>的臨立會2.0。<br />\n<br />\n所有接受委任的議員都是極權政府的幫兇、一員。<br />\n<br />\n如今開了中央直接委任的先例，一年後亦可重施故技，逐步建立萬年議會。<br />\n<br />\n請五眼聯盟對<span class=\"large\"><span class=\"red\">所有</span></span>留任議員施以制裁。<br />\n<br />\n大家一定覺得我痴撚線。要求外國用地圖炮。<br />\n但我只記得：<br />\n<span class=\"large\"><span class=\"red\"><span class=\"x-large\">若我們接受了政府的條件<br />\n我們已死去的朋友是不會原諒我們的。</span></span></span><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kYpSXik.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkYpSXik.jpg&h=0ad04afa&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ee9bd68427e477e16deef62417594204a8b643d1","tid":2165694,"uid":217430,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T03:55:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2896e983937b9f88beced5842de697576740434e","tid":2165694,"uid":217430,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T03:58:26.000Z","msg":"成班撚人留係議會就阻止倒惡法?訓撚醒未"},{"pid":"b0a6da10308729a63a51bc286a64050e71402bb7","tid":2165694,"uid":217430,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T04:01:41.000Z","msg":"